# 🤖 AI Voice + Chat Agent – BFSI SMEs

This repository contains my **Product Management case study deck** on an **AI-powered Voice + Chat Agent** designed for BFSI SMEs.  

---

## 📌 Problem
- SMEs in BFSI face high costs and inefficiencies in customer support.  
- Limited automation adoption due to integration complexity.  

---

## 💡 Solution
- Designed an AI-first assistant with:  
  - CRM integration  
  - Emotion detection  
  - Plug-and-play deployment  
- Targeting India’s $8B+ support automation market.  

---

